 \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neoplatonism\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996248334, \"rank\": 3.7509463956631467e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Trianon\", \"score\": 0.9993652802285773, \"rank\": 0.0005849996044233098, \"text\": \"Trianon\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Trianon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Trianon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They earned bragging rights and will now embark on a year-long partnership with Jordan Brand.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999991946277592, \"rank\": 8.053728980527003e-07, \"text\": \"Jordan Brand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This tournament harkens back to the very origins of the Jumpman, inspired by Michael Jordan's legendary 1v1 backyard battles against his brother, Larry.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jumpman_(video_game)\", \"score\": 0.5146485274671633, \"rank\": 0.7188090737237761, \"text\": \"Jumpman\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jumpman_(video_game)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jumpman_(video_game)\"}, {\"begin\": 598, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.055041444917114e-27, \"text\": \"Michael Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was through his unrelenting pursuit to win \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 despite matchups that often ended in defeat \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 that he created a legacy of greatness that changed the game of basketball forever.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the summer, players from across the globe competed for a spot in The One Finals, which included participants from Shanghai, Los Angeles, New York, Paris, and several other cities.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.9998088540768171, \"rank\": 0.00019118213298035657, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\"}, {\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999815542938026, \"rank\": 1.8445961049623008e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999916469613331, \"rank\": 8.35251265886356e-06, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996248334, \"rank\": 3.7509463956631467e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As they went head to head on their home courts, qualifying players moved onto The One Finals to face off at Jordan Brand's new home court in the 18th arrondissement.\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999991946277592, \"rank\": 8.053728980527003e-07, \"text\": \"Jordan Brand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The neighborhood is home to the Brand's global sport and cultural hub, District 23, which blends the area's rich cultural heritage with the excitement of basketball.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the competition concluded, Jordan Brand welcomed hip-hop artists Rema and Fat Joe for exclusive performances that further interlaced sport and culture as part of the brand's ongoing programming inside District 23.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999991946277592, \"rank\": 8.053728980527003e-07, \"text\": \"Jordan Brand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses_Isserles\", \"score\": 0.9999981226400793, \"rank\": 1.8773633650677525e-06, \"text\": \"Rema\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2566598\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses_Isserles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses_Isserles\"}, {\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\", \"score\": 0.9986102465415928, \"rank\": 0.0013098974594203095, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Jonas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Am